transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji.
Executive: Sir, aapne send nahi kiya tha wo documents?
Executive: Aapne bola tha na send karwane ke liye. Uday bol raha hu sir IndiaMART se.
Customer: Achcha achcha achcha achcha achcha.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Arre yaar main bahar aaya tha. Unse do teen baar call ho gaya tha. Maine bhej do bhej do bhej do. Asal mein unhi ka number hai, unhi ki email ID hai, unhi ka sab kuch hai.
Executive: Achcha achcha achcha. Bol dijiye sir nahi to service bhi deactivate ho jayegi aapki tab tak ke liye, kuch time ke liye.
Customer: Kitne time ke liye ho sakti hai?
Executive: Ek baar haan aap bata dijiye ek baar unse documents bhej denge to yahan hum laga denge isme jo documents aapko bataya tha. Ek baar baat kar lijiye aap unse.
Customer: Chalo shaam tak main bhijwa dunga aaj to main.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai sir. Thank you. Theek hai.
Customer: Iska karwa dena.
